<https://ontologia.segittur.es/turismo/def/core#Excursionist> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Person who travels but does not spend the night in a main destination other than their usual environment, for any main purpose other than to be employed by an entity resident in the country or place visited."@en .
<https://ontologia.segittur.es/turismo/def/core#Excursionist> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Persona que viaja pero no pernocta en un destino principal distinto al de su entorno habitual, con cualquier finalidad principal que no sea la de ser empleado por una entidad residente en el país o lugar visitado."@es .
<https://ontologia.segittur.es/turismo/def/core#Excursionist> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "excursionist"@en .
<https://ontologia.segittur.es/turismo/def/core#Excursionist> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "excursionista"@es .
