<https://ontologia.segittur.es/turismo/def/core#TourismResource> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Place, site or element that has a significant and attractive value for tourists and is capable of motivating their movement. They are often noted for their scenic beauty, historical importance, cultural uniqueness, or recreational value."@en .
<https://ontologia.segittur.es/turismo/def/core#TourismResource> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Recurso turístico"@es .
