<https://ontologia.segittur.es/turismo/def/core#YatchingPort> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf> <https://ontologia.segittur.es/turismo/def/core#SportFacility> .
<https://ontologia.segittur.es/turismo/def/core#YatchingPort> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Instalación ubicada en una zona costera o junto a un cuerpo de agua, que se utiliza para el amarre y resguardo de embarcaciones de recreo y deportivas, como yates, veleros, lanchas y otros tipos de barcos privados."@es .
<https://ontologia.segittur.es/turismo/def/core#YatchingPort> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Installation located in a coastal area or next to a body of water, which is used for mooring and sheltering recreational and sports vessels, such as yachts, sailboats, motorboats and other types of private boats."@en .
<https://ontologia.segittur.es/turismo/def/core#YatchingPort> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "puerto deportivo"@es .
<https://ontologia.segittur.es/turismo/def/core#YatchingPort> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "yachting port"@en .
